chapters.title: Base Version
chapters.description: Practice typing all lowercase letters without using the Shift key to build confidence and get familiar with essential keys. This is the best starting point for beginners or those just learning typing skills, helping to improve speed and accuracy.

chapters.title: Shift Version
chapters.description: Move on to typing uppercase letters using the Shift key to enhance accuracy and speed. This is a great next step after completing Chapter 1, where you’ll learn proper Shift key usage with confidence, an essential skill for mastering complete and efficient typing.

chapters.title: Numbers Course
chapters.description: You'll gain proficiency in typing the entire number row. Completing this chapter, along with Chapters 1 and 2, is required for your typing certificate. Mastering the number row boosts efficiency and accuracy in data entry.

chapters.title: Special Symbols
chapters.description: You'll gain proficiency by learning and practicing the special symbol keys on the keyboard, which are essential for typing accuracy. This chapter is required for your typing certificate, ensuring mastery of all essential skills.

chapters.title: Base Version
chapters.description: Agar aap urdu ki typing me bilkul new hen, yaa apni bunyaadi typing skills ko mazboot karna chahte hain, to BASE-VERSION behtareen nuqtaye aghaaz he. Is chapter ke andar aap keyboard ke tamam lower-case letters ki practice karenge..

chapters.title: Shift Version
chapters.description: Is chapter ke andar aap keyboard ke tamam keys ko Shift Key ke saath practice karenge. ye chapter aapke Base Version ko mazeed strong banane or Shift key ke usage ki practice me aham kirdaar ada karta he.

chapters.title: Numbers Course
chapters.description: Ye Chapter specially Number's Row ke liye designe kiya gaya he. yaani iske andar aap keyboard ke Number row ki mukammal practice karenge. ye chapter bhi Base version or Shift version ki tarha Certificate ke liye zaruri he..

chapters.title: Base Version
chapters.description: 'iidha kunt jdydan tmaman fi alkitabat biallughat al'ardiati, 'aw targhab fi taeziz maharatik al'asasiat fi alkitabati, fa'iina al'iisdar al'asasia ladayh niqat 'afdali. biaitibae hadha alfasl sawf tatadarab ealaa jamie alhuruf alsaghirati.

chapters.title: Shift Version
chapters.description: 'athna' mururik bihadha alfasli, satatadarab ealaa jamie mafatih lawhat almafatih bial'iidafat 'iilaa miftah SHIFT. yaleab hadha alfasl dwran mhman fi taqwiat almatahat 'aw altadarub ealaa aistikhdam miftah SHIFT 'athna' tashghil al'iisdar al'asasii.

chapters.title: Numbers Course
chapters.description: tama tasmim hadha alfasl khsysan lisafi al'arqami. 'ay 'anah biaistikhdam hadha satahsul ealaa tamrin mithaliin lisafi al'arqam fi lawhat almafatih, bihayth yumkinuk kitabat al'arqam bisuhulatin. wahadha alfasl daruriun aydan lilshahadati.

chapters.title: Special Symbols
chapters.description: laqad tama tasmim hadha alfasl lijamie alrumuz alkhasati, 'ay 'anah 'athna' tasafuhik lilfasl sawf tatadarab ealaa jamie almafatih alkhasat 'athna' aistikhdam lawhat almafatihi. watadhakur 'ana hadha alfasl daruriun aydan lilshahadati..
